During your opponent's turn: You can banish this card from your Graveyard; excavate the top card of your Deck, and if it's a Normal Trap Card, Set it to your side of the field, also you can activate it this turn (this is a Quick Effect). Otherwise, send it to the Graveyard. If this card is sent to the Graveyard: You can look at the top 3 cards of your Deck, then place them on the top of your Deck in any order. You can only use each effect of "Absolute King Back Jack" once per turn.
